  "title": "Project Manager",
  "description": "<p><strong>Primary Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Oversee end-to-end POC delivery within agreed timeline and budget parameters</li>\n  <li>Coordinate stakeholder engagement including clients and technical teams</li>\n  <li>Ensure deliverable quality meets government standards</li>\n  <li>Establish project governance framework and reporting mechanisms for government oversight</li>\n  <li>Facilitate risk management and issue escalation procedures</li>\n  <li>Coordinate live clients sitting testing and user acceptance activities</li>\n  <li>Ensure compliance with government procurement and project management methodologies</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Required Experience and Qualifications</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Minimum 7 years project management experience delivering government technology projects</li>\n  <li>Knowledge of Singapore Government procurement processes and contract management</li>\n  <li>Experience managing projects within GCC environments and government security constraints 1 year as Project Manager</li>\n  <li>Understanding of IM8 compliance requirements and government risk management frameworks</li>\n  <li>Proven track record delivering projects for government agencies</li>\n  <li>Experience in managing projects involving real-time systems and live operational environment Ship-HATS products</li>\n  <li>Experience in delivering GenAI features in GCC would be preferred</li>\n</ul>",
